editorialNotes.standard: Whether youre a local or just visiting, music fans neednt gamble on securing tickets to the hottest concerts and festivals in the UK. From monster headliners at Londons O2 Arena to an up-and-coming songstress at a corner club, Dice connects fans to their favorite musical acts with a slick, beautiful app that makes booking tickets a snapand without additional fees. Sold-out show? Just hop on the waiting list and get an alert if tickets become available.
